modName: PKPresets- Beautiful Ladies of Skyrim for RaceMenu
summary: Some beautiful female presets for a Dovahkiin worth playing as! Sass not included.
descriptionHtml:
[u][b][color=#00ff00][size=5]PKPresets- Beautiful Ladies of Skyrim.
[/size][/color][/b][/u][size=3]Just some presets I threw together. This is my first mod, and I hope you guys like it.
[img]http://static-3.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/71274-2-1447098345.jpg[/img]
[img]http://static-3.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/71274-4-1447098345.jpg[/img]
[img]http://static-3.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/71274-0-1447097955.jpg[/img]
[img]http://static-3.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/71274-5-1447098345.jpg[/img]
[img]http://static-3.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/71274-8-1447098345.jpg[/img]
[img]http://static-3.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/71274-9-1447098345.jpg[/img]
[img]http://static-3.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/71274-7-1447098345.jpg[/img]
[img]http://static-3.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/71274-6-1447098345.jpg[/img]
[/size]You will need:
RaceMenu by Expired
SKSE by silverlock
Ethereal Elven Overhaul by Nuska
Apachii Sky Hair- Main and Female by Apachii
True Eyes by JimtownIrish
The Eyes of Beauty by Gabriel Mailhot
KS Hairdos Renewal by Stealthic Khaos and Shocky

Mods I used:
SG female textures renewal
CBBE Curvy with NeverNude
ENB- Can't remember what preset
Painterly Warpaints

Don't forget to download, endorse and submit an image, I'd love to see these ladies' insane adventures.

[font=Comic Sans MS][size=6]Remember to give me feedback!!!! If you like this mod endorse it and tell me what you like in the comments!!![/size]
[/font]
[size=4]Thank you so much, be kind to eachother and most importantly, happy modding!
[/size][b][font=Comic Sans MS][color=#1e84cc][size=4]-Phoebe.K

[/size][/color][/font][/b]FAQ:
Q: This mod sucks I hate you.
A: That's not a question. Every mod is flawed in some way, like Thor's cape in this GIF image.
[img]http://media1.giphy.com/media/7peuZD6EX1y3m/200.gif[/img]
Q: Where the hell do I put it help meeeeeeeeee?????!!!!!!!
A: Your main directory is in (On windows 8): Windows (C:)>Program Files [u](x86)[/u]>Steam>SteamApps>common>Skyrim
